des: Listen to the audio stream of the National Federation of the Blind of Maryland to hear events, activities, programs, and advocacy work in the state of Maryland. The National Federation of the Blind of Maryland is a community of members and friends who believe in the hopes and dreams of the nation’s blind. Every day we work together to help blind people live the lives they want. Learn more by visiting: www.nfbmd.org.
